1. Standard Airdrop
Isme users ko sirf apna wallet address register karna hota hai.
Iske liye koi paisa kharch karne ki zaroorat nahi hoti, bas ek naya account banana padta hai.

2. Holder Airdrop
Ye airdrop un logon ko milta hai jinke paas pehle se koi khas coin (jaise Bitcoin ya Ethereum) hota hai.
Agar aapne apne Hardware Wallet ya Paper Wallet mein coins hold kiye hain, toh aapko naye tokens muft milte hain.

3. Bounty Airdrop
Isme users ko kuch asaan "tasks" karne padte hain, jaise Twitter par project ko follow karna ya Telegram group join karna.
In tasks ke badle mein unhe reward ke taur par tokens milte hain.

4. Fork Airdrop (Chain Split)
Jab ek blockchain split hoti hai (jaise Bitcoin se Bitcoin Cash), toh purane holders ko naye chain par barabar मात्रा mein naye coins milte hain.
Is tarah ke airdrops ko claim karna Cold Wallets (Hardware/Paper) par sabse aasaan aur surakshit hota hai.

5. Exclusive Airdrop
Ye sirf un "loyal" users ko milta hai jo kisi project ko bahut pehle se use kar rahe hain.
Inhe aksar "Retroactive Airdrops" bhi kaha jata hai.